==In Arda==
* {{TA|3001}}:
** The day after [[Bilbo's Farewell Party|the Birthday Party]], [[Frodo Baggins|Frodo]] manages the inheritance of [[Bilbo Baggins|Bilbo]]'s belongings and distributes his parting gifts. 
**The rumor spreads crowds of hobbits come to loot [[Bag End]] and seek treasure; including the [[Sackville-Bagginses]] who also demand to see Bilbo's will.
**At the evening [[Gandalf]] visits Frodo, warning him not to use [[One Ring|the Ring]] and keep it secret. He changes his plans<ref>{{FR|Party}}</ref> and begins seeking [[Gollum]].<ref>{{FR|Shadow}}</ref>
* {{TA|3018}}:
** Four [[Nazg没l|Riders]] enter [[the Shire]] before dawn. The others pursue the [[Rangers of the North|Rangers]] eastward, and then return to watch the [[Greenway]].
**[[Merry Brandybuck]] loads a cart with the remainder of [[Frodo]]'s luggage and leaves for [[Crickhollow]] with [[Fatty Bolger]].<ref name=comp>{{FR|Three}}</ref> 
** After lunch [[Folco Boffin]] leaves Frodo with Pippin. [[Lobelia Sackville-Baggins|Lobelia]] visits Bag End with [[Lotho Sackville-Baggins|Lotho]] to inspect.<ref name=comp/>
** [[Kham没l]] comes to [[Hobbiton]] at nightfall and interrogates [[Gaffer Gamgee]], who directs him to [[Buckland]]. Frodo leaves with Sam and Pippin.<ref name=comp/>
**The three hobbits walk west of Hobbiton, traverse [[the Water]], and after supper they join the road leading to [[Bucklebury]]. They camp in a [[fir]]-wood.<ref name=comp/>
** After taming [[Shadowfax]], [[Gandalf]] leaves [[Rohan]] and heads for [[Rivendell]].
